BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Jukebox Giants: Disco Fever!
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260719T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260719T170000
DTSTAMP:20260720T095228Z
UID:occ-926@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Cabaret
DESCRIPTION:A song-and-dance revue of disco hits — Donna Summer\, Bee Ge
 es\, and ABBA covers with a live band.\n\nA revue of 1970s disco hits\, wi
 th singers and dancers backed by a live band working through songs made fa
 mous by Donna Summer\, the Bee Gees\, ABBA\, and others. Expect sequins\, 
 choreography\, and a crowd on its feet by the second number. Presented by 
 the Strand Theatre. Note: the production may include flashing lights.
GEO:33.9536122;-84.5492054
LAST-MODIFIED:20260719T153608Z
LOCATION:The Strand Theatre\, 117 N Park Square
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://thestrand.my.salesforce-sites.com/ticket/#/instances/a0FPs0000
 06NoyLMAS
END:VEVENT
