BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Home for the Holidays: A Henry Players Revue
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261204T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261204T213000
DTSTAMP:20260720T095228Z
UID:occ-1384@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Cabaret
DESCRIPTION:A cabaret-style holiday revue with community performers of all
  ages — songs\, dance\, comedy skits\, and spoken word.\n\nA holiday rev
 ue in cabaret style\, back for its second year\, with community members of
  all ages taking the stage themselves. Expect a grab bag of seasonal acts:
  singing\, dancing\, comedy skits\, and spoken word. From the Henry Player
 s\, the volunteer community theatre company that has served Henry County s
 ince 1991.
GEO:33.4486439;-84.1418279
LAST-MODIFIED:20260720T095149Z
LOCATION:The Henry Players Theater\, 136 Hood St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.simpletix.com/e/home-for-the-holidays-a-henry-players-revu
 -tickets-271690
END:VEVENT
